   :verdict "HEADLINE (source available, the normal case): GRAPH 1 (HYPOTHETICAL) vs TEXT-on-source 3 — both correct, a COST win.
             SOURCE-UNAVAILABLE sub-case: text-on-lowered cannot recover the (Vec Claim) GENERIC fns (erase to 0) -> accuracy LOSS,
